1976
01:24:43,680 --> 01:24:44,900
 da vide da,

1977
01:24:44,900 --> 01:24:46,620
 neću reći,

1978
01:24:46,620 --> 01:24:47,460
 nabraja sad,

1979
01:24:47,460 --> 01:24:50,020
 ali ti velikani kad dođu.

1980
01:24:50,560 --> 01:24:53,400
 znači bilo je taki čudnija anegdota.

1981
01:24:53,400 --> 01:24:54,880
 Još jedna informacija,

1982
01:24:54,880 --> 01:24:56,760
 kad sam se već dotekao iz sajmišta,

1983
01:24:56,760 --> 01:24:59,100
 i moje obiteljske kuće,

1984
01:24:59,100 --> 01:25:00,820
